EAAB6ppltBWQBABGMsNiZAAJmZCbG2HVvJEGKrfY.description:
For 81 years, on a Saturday morning each Fall, one of Michigan's oldest traditions is on display on the corner of South University and Washtenaw. Every year since 1933, the same year President Ford played center for the national champion Wolverines, the University of Michigan community has celebrated the Michigan Mud Bowl. Even through a World War and an advent of Greek Life politics, this competitive rivalry game has been played every year. This year will be no different. Mudbowl is here.

The event has raised over $100,000 for C.S. Mott Children's Hospital in the last 5 years alone. We hope to raise a record amount this year in order to benefit those who need it most. Please feel free to donate below:

https://www.gofundme.com/ra4s7xcg

The 82nd Annual Michigan Mud Bowl will take place Saturday October 10 - see you all there
EAAB6ppltBWQBABGMsNiZAAJmZCbG2HVvJEGKrfY.name: 82nd Annual Michigan Mudbowl

EAAB6ppltBWQBABGMsNiZAAJmZCbG2HVvJEGKrfY.description:
AJ Marcus is an artist whose work blurs the line between photography and digital imaging. His processes involve the manipulation of captured images based on sensory stimulation: climate, music, nostalgia. He explores themes including the urban-rural dichotomy, youth, and worship of an idealized America. Notable work includes projects titled “The City Beautiful” and “…isms: an Interpretation”, both of which will be featured extensively at the show. 

Ezra Miller is a new media artist working with code as a way of creating images, interactive websites, and generative art. His projects live on the web, and his works explore topics including feedback, algorithmic phenomena, and the aesthetics of the digital world.

Come to Gallery 2 at the Latin School of Chicago between February 9th and 20th to see the show. There will be snacks and music as well as opportunities to talk with the artists during the reception on the 12th at 3:30. 

In addition, Ezra will be releasing his latest project titled “MY SHARDS” on February 12th in the form of an interactive website. Stay tuned.
EAAB6ppltBWQBABGMsNiZAAJmZCbG2HVvJEGKrfY.name: SENIOR ART SHOW: Ezra Miller & AJ Marcus
